B.a2c=new A.cl(B.a3f,[u.aR,"Category-indexed documents and reading rooms\u2014pair with Learn And Fun for study depth.",u.b_,"Advanced study lane\u2014research habits, depth reading, and scholarly rhythm.",u.d,"Ask Anything channel\u2014surface questions, follow threads, and invite answers.",u.f,u.aE,u.l,u.o,"Central library of AIR knowledge assets\u2014browse, filter, and open resources.","What AIR offers\u2014catalogue of products and services you can explore or request.",u.z,u.R,"Your schedule of AIR and profile events\u2014plan, confirm, and follow up.","Operational controls for what you steward\u2014teams, assets, or programmes.",u.L,u.X,"Official notices that affect you\u2014read, acknowledge, and archive.","Audit-style trails\u2014who did what, when\u2014so accountability stays crisp.",u.Z,"Recognition ledger\u2014credits, rewards, and redemption posture.",u.D,u.P,"Sensitive artefacts stay here\u2014treat as confidential by default.","What you are comfortable exposing publicly\u2014bios, showcases, open links.",u.M,"Pathways to belong\u2014roles, expectations, and how to plug into AIR properly.","Ideas, patches, content, or time\u2014channel contributions responsibly.",u.O,"Release notes and fresh capabilities\u2014skim what changed recently.","Reviewed irregularities\u2014closed items with rationale and owners.",u.bq,"Binary and threshold thinking\u2014where only zero-or-one decisions apply.","Channels, tone, and cadence\u2014keep communication intentional, not noisy.","Imagined futures and feature concepts\u2014brainstorm without breaking production.",u.r,"Light cultural content\u2014balance seriousness with restoration.",u.k,u.d1,u.cS,"Holistic systems view\u2014how parts interlock across AIR operations.",u.i,"Middle state\u2014rules, owners, and SLAs while work is underway.",u._,"Foundational narrative\u2014how AIR maps all-space and why it matters.",u.ck,u.y,"Graceful closures\u2014how to wind down initiatives without losing truth.","Cadence view\u2014anchor habits and deadlines to a humane calendar.",u.m,"Iterative refinement\u2014inspect outputs and tighten the next cycle.","Deliberate practice log\u2014reps, feedback, and specialisation depth.","Mutual aid posture\u2014share resources and care loops with your circle.","Closing gratitude and benedictions\u2014end sessions with clarity.",u.d7,"Persistence framing\u2014when to hold the line versus pivot smartly.",u.cX,"Own outcomes\u2014ledgers, promises, and transparent follow-through.","Whole-life design\u2014energy, ethics, and joy in the same frame.","Healthy social graph hygiene\u2014who you follow and why.","Harmony in groups\u2014roles, rhythm, and conflict repair.","Welcome path\u2014first tasks so new members feel oriented fast.","Warm protocols\u2014how AIR greets people across cultures and contexts.","Duty mapping\u2014what you owe to self, family, work, and community.",u.q,u.bz,"Background on the AIR Organisation itself\u2014charter and contact posture.",u.A,"Digitise products and records\u2014templates, scans, and structured capture.",u.bu,u.aT,u.da,u.bw,u.H,u.v,"Safety playbooks\u2014physical, digital, and emotional guardrails.","Care protocols\u2014hosting, healing touches, and dignified reception.",u.g,u.G,"Social graph hygiene\u2014groups, norms, and healthy boundaries.","R&D notebooks\u2014hypotheses, experiments, and reproducible notes.","Movement logistics\u2014trips, fleets, and transport coordination.","Identify gaps before they become incidents\u2014close loopholes early.","Where you have edge\u2014double down ethically and document why.",u.a,"Solution patterns\u2014playbooks that turn insight into shipped fixes.","Innovation pipeline\u2014from idea intake to validated prototypes.","Exploration mode\u2014customer discovery, field notes, and surprises.",u.W,"Forward narratives\u2014why effort still makes sense on bleak days.","Post-mortems and celebrations\u2014learn equally from both poles.","Spiritual practice space\u2014respectful, optional, and personal.",u.K,u.u,"Service mindset\u2014volunteer hours, seva logs, and community give-back.","Map important ties\u2014mentors, peers, dependents, and allies.",u.c9,"Time integrity\u2014SLAs, clocks, and respect for others\u2019 minutes.","Loyalty signals\u2014where you commit long term versus experiment.","Gratitude ledger\u2014thank people while memory is fresh.","Emotional intelligence drills\u2014feel with, not just for, others.","Forgiveness practice\u2014release without pretending harm never mattered.",u.Q,"Respect baselines\u2014titles, boundaries, and dignity defaults.","Discipline systems\u2014habits, streaks, and consequence design.","Healthy affection\u2014boundaries plus warmth in the same frame.",u.x,"Friend maintenance\u2014reach-outs, reciprocity, and depth checks.","Competitive tension\u2014when rivalry sharpens instead of corroding.","Fair competition\u2014rules, scoring, and recovery after contests.","Tech stack notes\u2014what you run, why, and upgrade windows.","Multilingual work\u2014glossaries, translators, and cultural nuance.","Mentor/monitor relationships\u2014cadence, goals, and feedback loops.","Investigations\u2014evidence chains with proportionate oversight.","Leadership posture\u2014vision, delegation, and follow-through.","Controls and coordination\u2014who pulls which levers, when.","Present-moment focus\u2014commit to one truthful path forward.","Trade lanes\u2014imports, exports, compliance, and counterparties.","Ranked lists\u2014priorities, leaderboards, and ordered decisions.","Numbers that matter\u2014distributions, trends, and honest baselines.","Peace and prosperity indicators\u2014community-level wellbeing view.","Global context\u2014regions, crises, and opportunities at planetary scale.",u.cJ,"Long-horizon growth\u2014add capacity slowly and compound kindly.","Media diet\u2014trusted sources, fact checks, and headline triage.","Engagement metrics\u2014events, RSVPs, and follow-up tasks.","Demos and walkthroughs\u2014show, don\u2019t only tell, your progress.","Facilitated discussions\u2014agendas, notes, and action items.","Scenario drills\u2014stimulus, response, and lessons captured.","Field tasks\u2014on-site work orders with proof of completion.","Interview guides\u2014questions, rubrics, and debrief templates.","Balanced evaluation\u2014merits and demerits on the same page.","Medical checks\u2014appointments, reports, and consent-aware storage.","Onboarding into services\u2014contracts, oaths, and first-week plans.","Rules corpora\u2014what is allowed, forbidden, and grey-zone.","Case files\u2014dockets, hearings, and counsel coordination (informational).","Election literacy\u2014platforms, timelines, and voter responsibility.","Leadership with heart\u2014policy plus empathy in public roles.","Spiritual content focused on Lord Shiva\u2014devotional and educational.","Inclusive prayer intentions\u2014peace, healing, and collective good.","Hopeful waiting\u2014track pending outcomes without losing agency.","Bilingual counting reports\u2014Hindi and English reporting rhythm."],t.li)
